Warning [L0201]: implicit clone of `p`; write `take p` to transfer ownership or `.clone()` to silence this warning
  --> tests/ui_lint/struct_implicit_clone.lex:12:10
    |
 12 |     show(p);
    |          ^
 Why: `show` expects to take ownership of this value
 Fix: write `take p` to move, or `p .clone()` to copy explicitly
